      "id": "PopularPost196157",
      "post_content": "I think you could make that argument for any color. Pro-![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) because red is chaotic and passionate. Pro-![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) because black is selfish and empowered, ergo cannot be reasoned with. But I agree. Pro-![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) is a bit of a stretch. If anything, I would think this would BE ![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol). From the flavor text, I think they were trying for more of a moral or ethical form of reasoning, not logical. But \"madness escaping\" sounds much more anti-black than blue to me.  \n  \nSeems to be a going theme that reason =/= blue:  \n[Nemesis of Reason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nemesis of Reason)  \n[Shield of Duty and Reason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Duty and Reason)",
      "posted_by": "OmegaSerris",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost196157\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I think you could make that argument for any color. Pro-<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> because red is chaotic and passionate. Pro-<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> because black is selfish and empowered, ergo cannot be reasoned with. But I agree. Pro-<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/> is a bit of a stretch. If anything, I would think this would BE <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Blue\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=U&amp;type=symbol\"/>. From the flavor text, I think they were trying for more of a moral or ethical form of reasoning, not logical. But \"madness escaping\" sounds much more anti-black than blue to me.<br/><br/>Seems to be a going theme that reason =/= blue:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nemesis of Reason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nemesis of Reason\">Nemesis of Reason</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shield of Duty and Reason\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield of Duty and Reason\">Shield of Duty and Reason</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '196157'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \